title: SXSW 2017 Panel with Ja Rule and DJ Envy
description: No explaining needed here! Tune-in to 30 minutes of straight fire with the legendary Ja Rule and The Breakfast Club's DJ Envy. So much fun getting on stage with these two and hashing out all things business, marketing, and culture during my 10 year anniversary at SXSW !! Make sure you check this one out!
